div1.p: Territory of Washington County of Spokane}ss.
In the District Court of the Territory of Washington and for the Fourth Judicial District thereof, holding terms at Cheney, Spokane County, in said Territory.
To the Sheriff of County, Greeting:

In the name of the United States, You are hereby commanded to summon Galow D.R. French A.B. Babb Dr. Pomeroy John Crane to be and appear before the District Court aforesaid at the Court House, in Cheney, in said County, on the forthwith day of April A.D. 188, at o'clock M. to there give evi- dence in the above entitled cause on the part of said Plaintiff

Witness the Hon. George Turner Associate Justice ofthe Supreme Court of Washington Territory, and Judge of said Court, and the Seal there- of affixed,this 16 day of April A.D. 1885 Kate W. Feuerbach Clerk. By R. Strobach Deputy.
Territory of Washington, County of Spokane ss.
I hereby certify that I served the within Subpoena on the within named witness by reading the same to each of them in said County, on this 17th day of April A.D. 1885 E.F. Whittier Sheriff By Deputy
In the District Court of the Territory of Washington, and for the First Judicial District thereof, holding Terms at Cheney, Spokane County, in said Territory.
Returned and Filed this 20 day of April A.D. 1885 Kate W. Feuerbach Clerk. By R. Strobach Deputy.
SHERIFF'S FEES Serving 5 names at 40 2.00 Mileage 40 miles at 10 4.50 Total, ----$6 50/1000
